nodes.text: WED-9-M1 was a model of droid visually similar to the WED Treadwell repair droid. A WED-9-M1 was present in the spaceport of Mos Eisley on Tatooine in 0 BBY.

The WED-9-M1 first appeared in the 1977 original trilogy film, Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope. The droid was first identified in "Every Droid in Star Wars" a video released in 2019 by the Star Wars Kids YouTube channel. The name originated in the Star Wars Legends continuity, where it was originally used by the Star Wars Customizable Card Game.
